<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,935,1430]" pageId="3" pageNumber="249">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,335,935,961]" pageId="3" pageNumber="249">Coloration.</emphasis>
Body yellowish brown, mottled with dark brown and black stripes. The apex of the two conical tubercles black. Face with four indistinct longitudinal stripes. All legs with dark brown annular stripes, hind femora with irregular brown stripes.
</paragraph>
